---
import Site from "~/layouts/Site.astro";
import Lang from "~/components/Lang.astro";
import { localizedPath } from "~/lib/i18n";
// SSR (not prerender) so the corrections email comes from runtime env.
// CDN caches the rendered page; see Cache-Control below.
// EDIT-ME: editorial-standards copy is template default. Customize section
// bodies to match your own selection / AI-usage policy.
export const prerender = false;
const lang = Astro.locals.lang ?? "zh";
const L = (p: string): string => localizedPath(p, lang);
const correctionsEmail = Astro.locals.runtime?.env?.CORRECTIONS_EMAIL
  ?? Astro.locals.runtime?.env?.CONTACT_EMAIL
  ?? "";
Astro.response.headers.set(
  "Cache-Control",
  "public, max-age=300, s-maxage=86400, stale-while-revalidate=86400",
);
---
<Site
  title="编辑标准 · Editorial standards — Glean · 拾遗"
  description="What 'every link human-reviewed' actually involves."
>
  <section class="page-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow"><Lang zh="编辑标准" en="Editorial standards" /></span>
      <h1 style="margin-top: 12px"><Lang zh="“人审”的具体含义" en="What “human review” means" /></h1>
      <p><Lang zh="“每条人审” 到底在审什么 · AI 能改什么 · 什么不能。" en="What “every link human-reviewed” actually involves · what AI may touch · what it can’t." /></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section--tight">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="standards-prose prose-block">
        <h2><Lang zh="1 · 什么会被选上" en="1 · What gets in" /></h2>
        <div class="yn-table">
          <div class="yn-yes">
            <h4><Lang zh="✓ 进" en="✓ Accepts" /></h4>
            <ul>
              <li><Lang><Fragment slot="zh">有<strong>新论点</strong>或<strong>新数据</strong>的工程内容</Fragment><Fragment slot="en">Engineering content with a <strong>new claim</strong> or <strong>new data</strong></Fragment></Lang></li>
              <li><Lang><Fragment slot="zh">作者是<strong>第一手</strong>实施者</Fragment><Fragment slot="en">Author is the <strong>first-hand</strong> implementer</Fragment></Lang></li>
              <li><Lang zh="官方 changelog / 设计文档 / RFC" en="Official changelogs / design docs / RFCs" /></li>
              <li><Lang><Fragment slot="zh">深度复盘文章 / 工程事故 postmortem</Fragment><Fragment slot="en">Postmortems &amp; retrospective deep-dives</Fragment></Lang></li>
              <li><Lang zh="非英文一手内容 (中 / 日 / 德 …)" en="First-hand non-English sources (CN / JP / DE …)" /></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="yn-no">
            <h4><Lang zh="✗ 拒" en="✗ Rejects" /></h4>
            <ul>
              <li><Lang zh="Listicle “10 best …”" en="Listicles (“10 best …”)" /></li>
              <li><Lang zh="Medium 转发文 / 内容农场" en="Medium re-blogs / content farms" /></li>
              <li><Lang zh="“AI 替你总结了…” 的 AI 摘要文" en="AI-summarized AI-summary posts" /></li>
              <li><Lang zh="付费墙后 80% 的文章" en="Articles 80% behind a paywall" /></li>
              <li><Lang zh="明显的 affiliate / SEO link farm" en="Obvious affiliate / SEO link farms" /></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2><Lang zh="2 · AI 在我们流程里能做什么" en="2 · What AI is allowed to do" /></h2>
        <p><Lang><Fragment slot="zh">DeepSeek 在我们流程里只做<strong>三件事</strong>：抓正文、双语翻译、起草要点。它<strong>不</strong>决定选稿，<strong>不</strong>写编辑点评，<strong>不</strong>排序周刊。它的草稿在编辑面板里全部是<em>可编辑的</em>，发布前会被人改一遍——平均 60% 的卡片会被改至少一处。</Fragment><Fragment slot="en">DeepSeek does exactly three things: extracts the body, translates both ways, drafts bullet points. It does <strong>not</strong> select picks, write editor’s notes, or order the weekly. Its drafts are all editable in our admin panel — on average 60% of cards get at least one human edit before publish.</Fragment></Lang></p>

        <div class="principles-grid">
          <div class="principle">
            <div class="principle__head">AI · YES</div>
            <h3 class="principle__title"><Lang zh="起翻译草稿" en="Translation draft" /></h3>
            <p class="principle__body"><Lang><Fragment slot="zh">英中互译的第一稿。编辑会校对术语和语气。</Fragment><Fragment slot="en">First-pass EN↔ZH. A human checks term &amp; tone.</Fragment></Lang></p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <div class="principle__head">AI · NO</div>
            <h3 class="principle__title"><Lang zh="编辑点评" en="Editor’s note" /></h3>
            <p class="principle__body"><Lang zh="“为什么读这一条”始终由人写。AI 永远不替编辑表态。" en="“Why read this” is always human-written. AI never takes a stance for us." /></p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <div class="principle__head">AI · NO</div>
            <h3 class="principle__title"><Lang zh="选稿决策" en="Selection" /></h3>
            <p class="principle__body"><Lang><Fragment slot="zh">AI 可以给候选打 importance/novelty 分供编辑参考，但<strong>最终选 / 拒由编辑按下按钮</strong>。</Fragment><Fragment slot="en">AI may score candidates as a reference. <strong>Pick / reject is always a human click.</strong></Fragment></Lang></p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <div class="principle__head">AI · YES</div>
            <h3 class="principle__title"><Lang zh="标签建议" en="Tag suggest" /></h3>
            <p class="principle__body"><Lang zh="从现有 tag 表里选 1-3 个。编辑可全部替换。" en="Picks 1–3 from existing taxonomy. Editor may replace all." /></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2><Lang zh="3 · 利益冲突" en="3 · Conflicts of interest" /></h2>
        <p><Lang><Fragment slot="zh">如果编辑或贡献者跟某条新闻的作者 / 公司有<strong>雇佣 / 顾问 / 投资关系</strong>，会在那条卡片底部加一行 <em>编辑披露</em>。我们不收任何形式的“推广费”——如果有，会在 /about 公告。</Fragment><Fragment slot="en">If an editor or contributor has an <strong>employment / advisory / investment</strong> relationship with the author or company of a pick, the card carries an <em>editor’s disclosure</em> line at the bottom. We take zero paid promotion — and we’d announce it on /about if we ever did.</Fragment></Lang></p>

        <h2><Lang zh="4 · 纠错与下架" en="4 · Corrections &amp; takedowns" /></h2>
        <blockquote>
          {correctionsEmail ? (
            <Lang>
              <Fragment slot="zh">发现错误？发邮件到 {correctionsEmail}。<br />技术细节有误 24 小时内修订并在文末标注；事实性错误重发勘误。</Fragment>
              <Fragment slot="en">Spot something wrong? Email {correctionsEmail}.<br />Technical mis-statements fixed within 24h with a footnote; factual errors trigger a corrigendum.</Fragment>
            </Lang>
          ) : (
            <Lang>
              <Fragment slot="zh">发现错误？通过站点页脚的联系方式告知。技术细节有误 24 小时内修订并在文末标注；事实性错误重发勘误。</Fragment>
              <Fragment slot="en">Spot something wrong? Reach out via the site footer. Technical mis-statements fixed within 24h with a footnote; factual errors trigger a corrigendum.</Fragment>
            </Lang>
          )}
        </blockquote>

        <h2><Lang zh="5 · 做不到的事" en="5 · What I won’t pretend to do" /></h2>
        <p><Lang><Fragment slot="zh">这不是“全栈技术媒体”。覆盖<strong>系统 · 工具 · 设计</strong>三个领域；硬件 / 学术论文 / 创业新闻 不在范围内。</Fragment><Fragment slot="en">This isn’t full-stack tech media. Coverage: <strong>systems · tooling · design</strong>. Hardware, academic papers, startup news — out of scope.</Fragment></Lang></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Site>
